<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الَّليْل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٠:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَأَمَّا مَنْ بَخِلَ وَاسْتَغْنَى <span class="c2">(٨)</span> وَكَذَّبَ بِالْحُسْنَى <span class="c2">(٩)</span> فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْعُسْرَى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> وَمَا يُغْنِي عَنْهُ مَالُهُ إِذَا تَرَدَّى <span class="c2">(١١)</span> إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا لَلْهُدَى <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلْآخِرَةَ وَالْأُولَى <span class="c2">(١٣)</span> فَأَنْذَرْتُكُمْ نَارًا تَلَظَّى <span class="c2">(١٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[الليل: ٨ - ١٤]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَكَذَّبَ بِالحُسْنَى}</span>: <span class="c2">«بِالخَلَفِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَرَدَّى}</span>: <span class="c2">«مَاتَ»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{تَلَظَّى}</span>: <span class="c2">«تَوَهَّجُ»</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَقَرَأَ عُبَيْدُ بْنُ عُمَيْرٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«تَتَلَظَّى»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>